'''扭叶松'''（学名：''Pinus contorta''；英语：lodgepole pine、shore pine、twisted pine<ref name=GRIN>{{GRIN |id=28435 |name=Pinus contorta}}</ref>、contorta pine），又名'''美国黑松'''、'''小干松'''，是[[松属|松属]]的一种常绿乔木，高1-3米，分布于北美洲西部沿海和山地<ref name="Moore2008">{{cite book |author1=Moore, Gerry |author2=Kershner, Bruce |author3=Craig Tufts |author4=Daniel Mathews |author5=Gil Nelson |author6=Spellenberg, Richard |author7=Thieret, John W. |author8=Terry Purinton |author9=Block, Andrew |title=National Wildlife Federation Field Guide to Trees of North America |publisher=Sterling |location=New York |year=2008 |page=91 |isbn=978-1-4027-3875-3}}</ref>，但少见于低地雨林<ref name="Sullivan2015">{{cite web | url= http://www.wildflowersearch.com/search?&PlantName=Pinus+contorta | last= Sullivan | first= Steven. K. | year= 2015 | title= ''Pinus contorta'' | website= Wildflower Search | accessdate= 2015-01-24 | archive-date= 2017-05-25 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170525105951/http://www.wildflowersearch.com/search?&PlantName=Pinus+contorta | dead-url= no }}</ref>。其种群数量依赖山火控制。

